it.polimi.deib.newdem.adrenaline.controller.actions.atoms.iteractions

Class InteractionStackImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.deib.newdem.adrenaline.controller.actions.atoms.iteractions.InteractionStackImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomsContainer, InteractionContext, InteractionStack

    public class InteractionStackImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements InteractionContext, InteractionStack
    An implementation of loosely based on Push Down Automata. This class presents itself as an InteractionContext to its inner interaction and as an InteractionStack to external classes.
